        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does Moz Pro's Domain Authority matter?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Domain Authority is useful for comparing sites against each other, but it's not a Google ranking factor. Use it to benchmark competitive positioning, not as an absolute health score. Sites with DA 40 routinely outrank DA 70 sites with superior content and technical fundamentals.</div>
